level 3
	shadow arts
		gain following as iniate, costing 2 ki points
			darkness, darkvision, pass without trace, silence
		gain minor illusion as inate

level 6
	shadow step
		new bonus action
			if standing in dim light or darkness
				teleport up to 60 feet to another spot with dim light or darkness
				get advantage on first melee attack before end of next turn

level 11
	cloak of shadows
		if in dim light or darkness
			new action
				cast invisibility on self
				also ends when entering bright light

level 17
	new reaction
		if adjacent foe is hit by someone else
			make melee attack against creature


